sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Auth as AuthController
    participant Poi as POIController
    participant Dup as DuplicateDetectionService
    participant Noti as NotificationService
    participant DB
    Client->>Auth: POST /api/auth/login
    Auth-->>Client: JWT
    Client->>Poi: POST /api/poi (Bearer JWT)
    Poi->>DB: Save POI (PendingReview for Saler)
    Poi->>Dup: CheckAndReportAsync(poi)
    Dup->>DB: Create duplicate report if matched
    Poi->>Noti: Notify admin on new POI
    Poi-->>Client: POI + duplicate warning
